<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三　長老之譬喻二</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十五　奢達品</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五〇　巴蘭伽達耶迦（座椅布施）</cb:mulu><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.175" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="16"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0243a" n="0243a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十六　槃多吉瓦迦品</cb:mulu><head>第十六　槃多吉瓦迦品</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五一　槃多吉瓦迦</cb:mulu><head>一五一　槃多吉瓦迦</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0243a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0243a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>淨如無垢月，清淨無煩擾，一切愛樂盡<note n="0243001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">以上一偈半出自 Sutta-nipāta 637。同處稱之為婆羅門，故取為對格。</note>，超越世執著。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0243a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0243a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>以淨眾人等，渡之並再度，森林佛思惟，安靜心鎮定。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0243a0801">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0243a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>槃多吉瓦迦，花朶蔓多奢，奉獻尸棄佛，世界具緣者。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0243a0901"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.176"></ref>四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0243a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>爾時作斯業，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0243a1001">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0243a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>從今百劫苦，名高而為王，其名稱徧眼<note n="0243002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Samantacakkhu（徧眼）。</note>，大力轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0243a1101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0243a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0243a1201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者槃多吉瓦迦長老寅唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0243a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0244a" n="0244a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五二　單巴普毘耶（赤銅色花）</cb:mulu><head>一五二　單巴普毘耶（赤銅色花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a0501">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0244a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾為犯罪者，勞動只為他，戰慄懷怖畏，奔竄林野境。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a0601">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0244a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>奔走見花朶，團簇美嬌艷，採得赤銅花，撒向菩提樹。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a0701">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0244a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>波吒釐花美，淨掃菩提樹，於菩提樹下，吾結跏趺坐。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a0801">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0244a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾往覓林徑，人眾來身邊，彼處見彼等，攝心向菩提。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a0901">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0244a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾心獲清淨，禮拜菩提樹，山嶮徑恐怖，墮落數陀羅<note n="0244001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 anekatāla papatiṁ（暹羅本）。</note><note n="0244002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">tāla 即 vitasti（搩），為長度之單位，vitasti = 12 anguli，為張開拇指與中指間之長度。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a1001">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0244a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>自吾獻花供，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供樹此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a1101">七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0244a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第三劫往昔，有王名觸者<note n="0244003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Samphusita（觸）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a1201">八</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0244a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0244a1301" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者單巴普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0244a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0245a" n="0245a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五三　義提山瑪奢迦（清掃道）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.177"></ref>一五三　義提山瑪奢迦（清掃道）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0245a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0245a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>光輝如朝日，黃金光閃耀，如月十五夜<note n="0245001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 pannarase yadā candaṁ（暹羅本）。</note>，世間導師出。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0245a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0245a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>六萬八千人，一切漏盡者，兩足人中長，圍繞正覺尊。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0245a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0245a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世之導師出<note n="0245002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">依暹羅本訂正為 niyyante。</note>，吾掃淨其道，更以清淨心，彼處樹幢幡。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0245a1101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0245a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾獻此幢幡，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，布施幡果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0245a1201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0245a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第四劫往昔，吾為大力王，望高呼善幡<note n="0245003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sudhaja（善幡）。</note>，吾常具此名。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0245a1301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0245a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0245a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0245a1401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者義提山瑪奢伽長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0246a" n="0246a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五四　格迦魯普奢伽（格迦魯供養）</cb:mulu><head>一五四　格迦魯普奢伽（格迦魯供養）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0246a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0246a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>生為神之子，供奉尸棄佛，採得迦魯花<note n="0246001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">kakkāru 天華之一。</note>，捧獻彼佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0246a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0246a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾獻彼花朶，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0246a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0246a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第九劫往昔，最勝有情王<note n="0246002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sattuttama（最勝有情）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0246a1101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0246a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0246a1201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者格迦魯普奢伽長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0246a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0247a" n="0247a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五五　曼陀羅瓦普伽奢（曼陀羅花供養）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.178"></ref>一五五　曼陀羅瓦普伽奢（曼陀羅花供養）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0247a0501">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0247a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>生為神之子，供養尸棄佛，以曼陀羅花<note n="0247001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">mandārava 譯為天妙華。</note>，捧獻彼佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0247a0601">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0247a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>七日如來前，常敷天花鬘，諸人皆來集，南無彼如來。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0247a0701">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0247a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>自吾供此花，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0247a0801">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0247a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第十劫之昔，名喚輝持王<note n="0247002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Jutindhara（輝持）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0247a0901">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0247a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0247a1001" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者曼陀羅瓦普奢伽宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0247a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0248a" n="0248a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五六　迦單巴普毘耶（迦曇婆花）</cb:mulu><head>一五六　迦單巴普毘耶（迦曇婆花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0248a0401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0248a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>雪山不遠處，有山屈屈吒<note n="0248001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Kukkuṭa（雞）。</note>，屈屈吒山麓，住有彼七佛<note n="0248002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 vasanti te（暹羅本）。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0248a0501">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0248a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>迦曇婆花放，如明王陽昇，吾採置兩掌，散撒彼七佛。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0248a0601">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0248a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾供此花朶，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0248a0701">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0248a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>九十二劫昔，七人花嚮導<note n="0248003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Phullanāyaka（花嚮導）。異本為 Pupphanāmakā（叫做花者）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0248a0801">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0248a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0248a0901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者迦單巴普庇耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0248a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0249a" n="0249a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五七　提那斯羅迦（提那斯拉花）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.179"></ref>一五七　提那斯羅迦（提那斯拉花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0249a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0249a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>雪山不遠處，普達格那山<note n="0249001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Bhūtagaṇa（鬼群）。</note>，彼處住勝者，去縛自存人。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0249a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0249a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>提那斯拉花<note n="0249002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">tiṇasūla 素馨之一種。</note>，吾捧獻供佛，九萬九千劫，吾不墮惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0249a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0249a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>於昔十一劫，有王達尼哈，大力七寶具，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0249a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0249a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0249a0701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者提那斯羅迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五八　那伽普毘耶（犬死出花）</cb:mulu><head>一五八　那伽普毘耶（犬死出花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0249a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0249a1401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0249a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>其名謂善犢<note n="0249001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Suvaccha（善積）。</note>，吠陀婆羅門，住於山狹間，弟子眾隨後。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0250a" n="0250a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0250a0101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0250a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>巴多穆塔拉，接受尊供物，為搖撼吾心，走近吾住居。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0250a0201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0250a0201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>上空佛經行，恰如燃燈明<note n="0250002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 dīpo pajjalate tathā（暹羅本）。</note>，認知吾心笑<note n="0250003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 hāsaṁ mama（暹羅本訂正為 mamaṁ）viditvāna（暹羅本）。</note>，指向東方去。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0250a0301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0250a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>其不可思議，身毛即豎立，吾取犬死花，撒向佛去路。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0250a0401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0250a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>由吾散此花<note n="0250004" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">從異本之 okiriṁ ahaṁ（暹羅本亦同）。</note>，從此十萬劫，吾心為清淨，永不生惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0250a0501">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0250a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>三千百劫昔，有王名大車<note n="0250005" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Mahāratha（大車）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0250a0601">七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0250a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0250a0701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者那伽普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0250a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0251a" n="0251a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五九　芬那伽普毘耶（芬那伽花）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.180"></ref>一五九　芬那伽普毘耶（芬那伽花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0251a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0251a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>入深於叢林，吾獵人居住，噴那伽花開，吾念勝佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0251a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0251a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>芳香馨郁馥，手折美艷花，砂丘作塔婆，捧花供養佛。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0251a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0251a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>自吾供鮮花，九十二劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0251a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0251a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>九十一劫昔，一王名驅闇<note n="0251001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Tamonuda（驅闇）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0251a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0251a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0251a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者芬那迦普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六〇　拘物無陀達耶迦（拘物頭布施）</cb:mulu><head>一六〇　拘物無陀達耶迦（拘物頭布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0251a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0251a1401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0251a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>雪山不遠處，彼處有大湖，鉢頭摩鉢羅，分陀利迦廣。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0252a" n="0252a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0252a0101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0252a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>爾時於彼處，吾為鷄冠鳥<note n="0252001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">kakudha 鷄冠之意，又作樹名。暹羅本為 kukkuṭa（鷄）。</note>，有德守業戒<note n="0252002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 vattasampanno（暹羅本）。</note>，明曉福非福<note n="0252003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">訂為 Puññāpuññesu kovido（依暹羅本）。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0252a0201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0252a0201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>巴多穆塔拉，受尊供養物，於湖不遠處，過彼大單尼。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0252a0301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0252a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>水採拘物頭<note n="0252004" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">從暹羅本讀為 bhitvā。</note>，捧獻彼大仙，彼知吾心意，牟尼受供養。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0252a0401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0252a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾行此布施<note n="0252005" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">訂正為 tañ ca dānam daditvā' haṁ（依暹羅本）。</note>，淨根所使故，十萬劫之間，不生於惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0252a0501">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0252a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>一千六百劫，婆留那八人，彼等具七寶，大力轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0252a0601"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.181"></ref>七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0252a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0252a0701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者拘無陀達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0252a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0253a" n="0253a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0253a0101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a02"/><lg xml:id="lgN29p0253a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:3em">槃多吉、單巴普毘、義提、格迦魯普庇耶、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a03"/><l style="text-indent:3em">曼陀羅與迦單巴、斯羅迦、那伽普毘耶、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a04"/><l style="text-indent:3em">芬那伽與拘無陀、十人宣偈五十六。</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
